CurrentOpen Payments API Endpoint

Source: R/S7_backend.R
CurrentOpen.Rd

CurrentOpen Payments API Endpoint

Usage

CurrentOpen(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <CurrentOpen> object.

Examples
